## Data License and Attribution

The Consumer Price Index (CPI) data used in this application is provided by Danmarks Statistik 
and is subject to their terms of use and attribution requirements.

### Data Source Attribution:
- Data provider: Danmarks Statistik (Statistics Denmark)
- Dataset: Forbrugerprisindeks (Consumer Price Index)
- Source URL: https://www.dst.dk/da/Statistik/emner/oekonomi/prisindeks/forbrugerprisindeks

### Data Usage Terms:
1. The data from Danmarks Statistik is used in accordance with their rules and regulations
   for data usage (https://www.dst.dk/da/TilSalg/data-til-forskning/regler-og-datasikkerhed).
2. This is an independent tool and is not affiliated with Danmarks Statistik.
3. The calculations and visualizations in this application are for informational purposes only.

## Disclaimer

THIS SOFTWARE AND THE ACCOMPANYING DATA VISUALIZATIONS ARE PROVIDED "AS IS", 
WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND. THE DEVELOPERS TAKE NO RESPONSIBILITY FOR ANY 
ERRORS OR MISTAKES IN THE CALCULATIONS. ALWAYS VERIFY IMPORTANT FINANCIAL 
DECISIONS WITH A QUALIFIED PROFESSIONAL.

No personal data or microdata is collected or processed. All salary data is 
stored locally in the user's browser and is not shared with any third parties. 